# module: eng.case
# status: planned
# purpose: per-case manifests for sample-to-run workflows.
#
# Current implementation:
#   no native case manifest module yet. Promoted sample tables with case_id
#   columns are summarized in typed_payload.sample_tables[] with duplicate-case
#   diagnostics and row-hash previews. Workflow examples still use explicit
#   external case_manifest.json files, generated files, process results, and
#   output manifests.
#
# Planned CaseManifest fields:
#   case_id
#   sample row hash
#   case directory
#   generated input files
#   process command and status
#   result files
#   metrics
#   failure reason
#   cache/resume status
#
# Non-goal:
#   loops that mutate files without a case manifest should not become the
#   preferred batch-workflow pattern.
